'''Life support capsules''' were containers which kept alive and, optionally, healed critically-wounded occupants. [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] used two such units to preserve [[Orman Tagge/Legends|Orman]] and [[Silas Tagge/Legends|Silas Tagge]] after their [[Mining Explorer|ship]] was depressurized.

